- Connor.

1:22:56.054 --> 1:22:56.923
- Ken, Ken!

1:23:02.200 --> 1:23:03.335
- Hello, sweetheart.

1:23:07.746 --> 1:23:09.080
Come back to bed.

1:23:10.149 --> 1:23:11.318
- Who the hell are you?

1:23:15.561 --> 1:23:17.397
- You know who I am.

