1:23:38.574 --> 1:23:41.579
That's the way to do it.

1:25:05.245 --> 1:25:07.818
Connor!

1:25:07.819 --> 1:25:11.592
- You're going to
miss the finale, Beth!

1:25:11.593 --> 1:25:12.425
- Where's your phone?

1:25:12.426 --> 1:25:13.696
- I left it in my room.

1:25:13.697 --> 1:25:15.365
We can't leave Connor!
- We have to!

1:25:15.366 --> 1:25:16.902
We need to get out of here.

1:25:16.903 --> 1:25:19.007
- Who are they, mom?
- I don't know!

1:25:19.008 --> 1:25:20.110
Where's the key?

1:25:21.478 --> 1:25:23.414
Where are you?

1:25:23.415 --> 1:25:26.487
He's coming, Beth!

1:28:57.142 --> 1:28:57.977
- Hey.

1:29:00.714 --> 1:29:01.885
Rectal reject.

1:29:48.677 --> 1:29:51.851
- That's the way to
do it, Mr. Punch.

1:29:54.322 --> 1:29:56.826
Isn't that right, Beth?

1:29:56.827 --> 1:29:58.831
That's the way to do it.

1:32:03.847 --> 1:32:05.450
- Listen to me.

1:32:07.922 --> 1:32:10.026
Just run, don't worry about me.

1:32:10.027 --> 1:32:11.862
I won't be far behind you.

1:32:13.133 --> 1:32:15.169
Get to Frank's
farm, call for help.

1:32:15.170 --> 1:32:16.438
- I'm not leaving without you.

1:32:16.439 --> 1:32:20.547
I said go!

1:33:11.016 --> 1:33:14.220
Beth.

1:33:14.221 --> 1:33:15.058
Beth.

1:33:23.707 --> 1:33:25.377
- I'm ready for you.

1:34:07.094 --> 1:34:08.561
Who are you?

1:34:08.562 --> 1:34:09.831
- There once was a girl.

1:34:11.368 --> 1:34:12.203
- Called Maude.

1:34:24.059 --> 1:34:27.134
- There once was a
girl called Maude.

1:34:31.109 --> 1:34:33.312
Who picked up a
strange creature.

1:34:40.993 --> 1:34:42.630
And brought it to her home.

1:34:51.182 --> 1:34:54.454
You need to be strong
now, for our daughter.

1:34:56.391 --> 1:34:58.828
Open your eyes.

1:35:24.148 --> 1:35:29.158
Finally, you are awake.

1:35:34.467 --> 1:35:35.303
Beth.

1:35:36.872 --> 1:35:37.707
My Beth.

1:35:40.980 --> 1:35:41.815
See, Beth.

1:35:42.917 --> 1:35:43.785
See.

1:35:45.990 --> 1:35:46.825
Now,

1:35:48.196 --> 1:35:49.265
now we dance.

1:36:18.256 --> 1:36:19.823
That's
the way to do it.

