That's the way to do it.

1:38:10.110 --> 1:38:12.014
- Nice work, Mr. Punch.

1:38:37.466 --> 1:38:38.368
- Surprise!

1:38:39.537 --> 1:38:41.204
Oh!

1:38:41.205 --> 1:38:44.311
- You have front row tickets.

1:38:45.682 --> 1:38:47.017
- Why are you doing this?

1:38:48.821 --> 1:38:53.061
Now Beth.

1:38:53.062 --> 1:38:56.803
Don't you just love the
randomness of it all?

1:38:58.106 --> 1:39:00.746
We did all this for you.

1:39:02.383 --> 1:39:06.221
We've listened to everything.

1:39:06.222 --> 1:39:08.058
- You like dragons.

1:39:08.059 --> 1:39:10.229
- I don't think we're
supposed to like dragons.

1:39:10.230 --> 1:39:11.065
- So lost.

1:39:13.638 --> 1:39:18.145
So perfect.

1:39:18.146 --> 1:39:21.285
The one we had always
been looking for.

1:39:23.289 --> 1:39:25.729
The raw material that artists

1:39:26.897 --> 1:39:29.804
